**Summary:** This documentation explains how to build Event Segmentation analyses in Amplitude, covering the Events Module for selecting events and properties, the Measured As Module for choosing measurement types, the Segmentation Module for defining user segments, and Y-axis customization options including dual Y-axis support for line charts.

